Back in the Olde Dayes I had a roommate who was stuck with a rotary (and
blown) engine Mazda that, even though complete, the wrecking yards
wouldn't touch.  He ended up removing the license and VIN plates and
parking it a couple of blocks down the street.  A few days later his
problem disappeared.

Our tax money at work!
